title: Lake Home Available For Lease In White Lake
posting_body: ["IF THIS PROPERTY DOESN'T FIT YOUR NEEDS, FEEL FREE TO CALL OR EMAIL ME", 'I MAY HAVE OTHER PROPERTIES TO PASS BY YOU', 'show contact info', '4 Bedrooms', '3.5 Baths', '3375 Square Ft', 'Fully renovated lake house on Cedar Island Lake (sports lake) that has been fully renovated with beautiful upgrades.', 'The house has new roof, windows, siding, kitchen with granite countertops and new appliance including wine cooler along with many other upgrades.', 'The property is on a peninsula which means water views from nearly everywhere in the home and the views are truly spectacular.', 'House features a two car garage, mud room, office, large kitchen with two islands and a spectacular pantry along with built in closets.', "The master bedroom has it's own sitting area with a balcony, a large walk in closet and a beautiful new bathroom.", 'Enjoy the Summer months by jumping in the lake right out of your backyard.', 'This is your chance to rent your dream home on the water!', 'The agent does not guarantee the accuracy of the square footage, lot size, or other information concerning the conditions or features of the property provided by the seller or obtained from public records or other sources.', 'The buyer is advised to independently verify the accuracy of all information through personal inspection and with appropriate professionals.', 'Presented by: Christopher Berna', 'Christopher Berna License #6501432997']
